data_investment_summary = (data_investment
  .melt(id_vars=["gvkey", "year"], var_name="measure",
        value_vars=["investment_lead", "cash_flows", "tobins_q"])
  .get(["measure", "value"])
  .groupby("measure")
  .describe(percentiles=[0.05, 0.5, 0.95])
)
np.round(data_investment_summary, 2)
```

