Inference:  iid
Observations:  130559

| Coefficient   |   Estimate |   Std. Error |   t value |   Pr(>|t|) |   2.5% |   97.5% |
|:--------------|-----------:|-------------:|----------:|-----------:|-------:|--------:|
| Intercept     |      0.042 |        0.000 |   128.821 |      0.000 |  0.041 |   0.043 |
| cash_flows    |      0.049 |        0.001 |    63.343 |      0.000 |  0.048 |   0.051 |
